ue of WinJS.Binding.optimizeBindingReferences.","pos":[18276,18336]},{"content":"Corrective Action","pos":[18342,18359]},{"pos":[18361,18439],"content":"Set WinJS.Binding.optimizeBindingReferences to <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>true<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> in the app JavaScript.","source":"Set WinJS.Binding.optimizeBindingReferences to **true** in the app JavaScript."},{"content":"App manifest resources test","pos":[18444,18471]},{"content":"App resources validation","pos":[18477,18501]},{"content":"The app might not install if the strings or images declared in your app’s manifest are incorrect.","pos":[18503,18600]},{"content":"If the app does install with these errors, your app’s logo or other images used by your app might not display correctly.","pos":[18601,18721]},{"content":"Test Details","pos":[18727,18739]},{"content":"Inspects the resources defined in the app manifest to make sure they are present and valid.","pos":[18741,18832]},{"content":"Corrective Action","pos":[18838,18855]},{"content":"Use the following table as guidance.","pos":[18857,18893]},{"pos":[18895,19031],"content":"Error message Comments The image {image name} defines both Scale and TargetSize qualifiers; you can define only one qualifier at a time.","source":"Error message\nComments\nThe image {image name} defines both Scale and TargetSize qualifiers; you can define only one qualifier at a time."},{"content":"You can customize images for different resolutions.","pos":[19033,19084]},{"content":"In the actual message, {image name} contains the name of the image with the error.","pos":[19086,19168]},{"content":"Make sure that each image defines either Scale or TargetSize as the qualifier.","pos":[19170,19248]},{"content":"The image {image name} failed the size restrictions.","pos":[19250,19302]},{"content":"Ensure that all the app images adhere to the proper size restrictions.","pos":[19304,19374]},{"content":"In the actual message, {image name} contains the name of the image with the error.","pos"